<div class="header-image jumbotron">
  <h1>Stations Overview</h1>
  <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/stations">All Stations</a></p>
</div>

<h3>Total count of stations: <%= Station.count %></h3>
<h3>Average bikes avaiable per station: <%= Station.average_bikes_per_station %>
<h3>Stations where the most bikes are available: <%= Station.most_bikes %></h3>
<h3>Most bikes available at a station:
  <ul>
   <% Station.find_by_most_bikes.each do |station| %>
    <li><%= station.name %>: <%= station.dock_count %></li>
  <% end %> 
  </ul> 
</h3>
<h3>Fewest bikes available at a station: <%= Station.fewest_bikes %></h3>
<h3>Stations where the fewest bikes are available:
  <ul>
   <% Station.find_by_fewest_bikes.each do |station| %>
    <li><%= station.name %>: <%= station.dock_count %></li>
  <% end %> 
  </ul>
<h3>Most recently installed station: <%= Station.most_recently_installed_station.name %></h3>
<h3>Oldest station: <%= Station.oldest_station.name %></h3>